# Marketing (Astro)

- **Canonical:** `apps/template/marketing` or `apps/<slug>/marketing`.
- **Structure:** `src/pages/*.astro`, `src/layouts/`, `src/components/`, SEO via `src/components/SeoHead.astro`, blog content under `src/content/blog/` when used.
- **Design system:** import `@yca-software/design-system` and `@yca-software/design-system/styles.css`; Tailwind `@source` may reference `packages/design-system` — keep paths valid after moves.
- **Validate:** `pnpm lint`, `pnpm build` (runs `astro check && astro build`) in the marketing package.
